K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-6: btsun mo'i 'khor gyi nang na 'dug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-7: bud med kyi tshogs kyis bskor cing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-14: rnga brdung zhing yid bde bar rtse dga' ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-15: dga' mgur spyod pa'ang 'chi bas 'jigs skrag nas shin tu yid mi bde zhing 'chi ba'i dus byed par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-17: de ltar khyod khyim gyi nang na spos dri zhim po'i bsku bas ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-24: 'bru mar dri zhim po dang ldan pa'i mar me ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-26: dar gyi lnga ldi mang po ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-28: me tog dri zhim po'i sil ma mang pos ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-40: yul ka lingka pa'i stan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138a-42: de'i steng du gding bas ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-0: g-yas g-yon du dar dmar @138b po'i sngas ni bzhag pa'i khri la nyal ba'ang bya rog dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-10: rang gi gnas mchog tu 'jigs su rung ba'i dur sa chen por bor nas lus g-yo ba med cing sa la nyal du gdon mi za'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-12: 'di ltar yang khyod glang po che'i bya la kha'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-19: rol mo sil snyan gyi bye brag len pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-23: rnam par rgyal ba'i ba dan ni; bsgreng /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-24: bsil yab nor bu'i yu bcan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-26: shing rta la las byas pa ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-30: dpung bu chung ngu ma ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-33: bram zes bslab pa phog pa'i blon po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-35: skye bo thal mo sbyar ba brgya stong du mas ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-36: phyag bya zhing rgyal bar sbyon cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:138b-38: ces snyan par brjod de phyir 'byung ba'ang ring po mi thogs par g-yo ba med cing mal du shi nas mi bzhis bteg ste pha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-0: grong khyer ba'i skye bo dag mya ngan gyi dbang du song ste lag pa btegs nas brang @139a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-1: brdung zhing mchog tu snying rje bar kyi hud bu /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-4: kyi hud jo bo zhes ngu zhing zhabs 'bring ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-5: grong khyer ba'i skye bo dag gis 'jigs pa dang bcas par mthong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-6: grong khyer gyi lho phyogs kyi sgor phyung nas sa'i 'og tu bcug gam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-7: 'brog dgon par sa'i 'og tu bcug kyang rung /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-10: wa la sogs pas zos shing rus pa de dag mes bsregs sam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-12: sa'i 'og tu bcug kyang rlung dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-14: char pas phye mar byas te phyogs phyogs su 'thor zhing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-15: de nyid du rul bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-17: de ltar sems can thams cad kyi lus kyang 'di bzhin du 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-22: de ltar yid brtan du mi rung ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-23: de ltar 'gyur ba'i chos can te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-35: mya ngan dang 'khrug pa mang ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-41: rnam par 'jig pa'i chos can no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-44: mi rtag par blta zhing zad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-45: dengs pa'i sgor blta bar bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139a-46: 'dod chags kyis ma chags pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-0: @139b zhe sdang gis mi sdang pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-1: gti mug gis ma rmongs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-2: rgyal srid kyi dbang phyug gi bde ba la ma chags pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-4: 'dod pa'i longs spyod kyi bde ba la ma chags pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-5: mi rtag par lta ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-11: srog snyems pa med par 'chi bas 'jigs skrag par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-12: chos kho nas rgyal srid gyis shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-15: khyod chos dang mthun par gyis shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-16: chos ma yin pa dang mthun par ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-24: sten pas 'dod pa dag gis ngoms par nga mi smra ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-25: gang dag 'phags pa'i shes rab kyis ngoms par 'gyur ba de dag ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-29: ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed rnams /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-30: 'du byed kyi rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-31: rnam par shes pa'i rkyen gyis ming dang gzugs /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-32: ming dang gzugs kyi rkyen gyis skye mched drug /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-33: skye mched drug gi rkyen gyis reg pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-34: reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-35: tshor ba'i rkyen gyis sred pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-36: sred pa'i rkyen gyis len pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-37: len pa'i rkyen gyis srid pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-38: srid pa'i rkyen gyis skye ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:139b-39: skye ba'i rkyen gyis rga shi dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-3: de ltar sdug bsngal gyi phung po chen po 'ba' zhig pa 'di'ang 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-4: de la ma rig pa 'gags pas 'du byed 'gag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-5: 'du byed 'gags pas rnam par shes pa 'gag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-6: rnam par shes pa 'gags pas ming dang gzugs 'gag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-7: ming dang gzugs 'gags pas skye mched drug 'gag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-8: skye mched drug 'gags pas reg pa 'gag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-14: skye ba 'gags pas rga shi dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-20: de ltar sdug bsngal gyi phung po chen po 'ba' zhig po 'di'ang 'gag par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-23: 'dod chags kyis ma chags pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-24: zhe sdang gis mi sdang ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-25: gti mug gis mi rmongs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-26: rgyal srid kyi dbang phyug dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-27: dbang gi dregs pa med par chos kho nas rgyal srid gyis shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-30: khyod chos dang mthun par gyis shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140a-31: chos ma yin pa dang mthun par ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-0: rgyal po chen @140b po; 'dod pa rnams kyi rnyed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-2: ngoms par mi 'gyur ba'i bar du nga smra ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-3: rab tu ngoms par mi 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-5: gang dag 'phags pa'i shes rab kyis ngoms par gyur pa de dag ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-7: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i tshe tshigs su bcad pa 'di dag bka' stsal to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-10: khyod kyi tshe 'di mi brtan gyi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-11: rgyal po bag med ma byed cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-12: nor ni gtang gi lus ni bsrung bar bya //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-13: yan lag gtang gi srog ni bsrung bar bya //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-14: nor dang yan lag rnams dang de bzhin srog /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-15: thams cad gtang gi 'dir ni chos bsrung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-16: chos spyod pa ni chos la srung bar byed //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-17: dper na dbyar dus gdugs chen srung ba bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-18: chos spyod pa yi phan yon 'di yin te; ;chos spyod pa ni ngan 'gror mi 'gro'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-19: chos ma yin pa spyod cing bag med pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-21: gang du gnas na 'chi bas mi tshugs pa'i //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-22: sa phyogs de ni yod pa ma yin te //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-23: bar snang ma yin rgya mtsho'i nang ma yin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-24: ri yi phug tu zhugs kyang mi phan no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-25: 'chi bas 'jigs pa chen po de dag ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-26: phung po 'jig cing srog 'gag shes gyis la; ;'chi med thob par khyod ni mos par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:140b-27: mya ngan 'das thob phyin chad 'chi mi 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:141a-0: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas yul ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal @141a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:141a-2: srog chags brgyad khri bzhi stong po de dag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:141a-7: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rang ste bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:141a-8: 'phags pa rgyal po la gdams pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:141a-9: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:141a-11: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba bandhe ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-063-002:141a-12: skad gsar cad kyis kyang bcos nas gtan la phab pa /
